dc_description_s: Relief shown by hachures and spot heights. Includes insets of Manilla region, Straits of Singapore and Java. From "Atlas Universel" by M. Vivien de Saint-Martin & Fr. Schrader. 1 map: col.; 43 x 53 cm This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
